  ## SAVANNAH SUNSET RESORT
  
  An overnight oasis offering exclusive panoramic views within our 350-acres Wild Safari which is home to over 1,200 animals from 6 continents.
  
  ## Savannah Sunset Resort
  
  Experience a getaway that redefines vacation expectations through unparalleled views and once in a lifetime experiences with accommodations featuring modern luxury with an exotic flare.
  
  Each luxury suite offers a private bathroom and access to outdoor entertainment, fire pits, restaurant & bar, spa services, event meeting space and more.
  
  Find the perfect suite for your preferred glamping experience.
  
  [Book Now](https://reservations.sixflags.com/savannahsunset/)
  
