  ### Included Resort Benefits
  
  ![Giraffe](https://www.sixflags.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fbsnrdz4t%2Fproduction%2F8ae80b50cc4edad987b74c05344fcc462662bc87-2560x1707.jpg%3Fw%3D628%26h%3D770%26q%3D80%26fit%3Dclip%26auto%3Dformat%26dpr%3D2&w=1920&q=75)
  
  Giraffe
  
  ## Giraffe Feeding
  
  Each day of your stay, feed and interact with our resident giraffes under the guidance of our wildlife experts.
  
  ![Wild safari truck full of guests driving pasta group of giraffes](https://www.sixflags.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fbsnrdz4t%2Fproduction%2Fad5f8699d1233d6673439328ad52124bb34acf5c-6000x4000.jpg%3Fw%3D628%26h%3D770%26q%3D80%26fit%3Dclip%26auto%3Dformat%26dpr%3D2&w=1920&q=75)
  
  Wild Safari Tour
  
  ## Wild Safari Tour
  
  Head out on a Savannah Sunset Resort & Spa-exclusive Wild Safari tour to get up close with the 1,200 animals.
  
  ![Guests riding a coaster at Six Flags](https://www.sixflags.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fbsnrdz4t%2Fproduction%2Fef23567fc5ebcd290a83b6b209493d492ba22cdc-2560x1709.jpg%3Fw%3D628%26h%3D770%26q%3D80%26fit%3Dclip%26auto%3Dformat%26dpr%3D2&w=1920&q=75)
  
  Resort Access
  
  ## Great Adventure Resort Access
  
  Guests will have access to all 3 parks that encompass Great Adventure Resort with a multi-park ticket included with each night of stay.
  
  ![Guests eating Breakfast](https://www.sixflags.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fbsnrdz4t%2Fproduction%2F296f6fbb4d204c2ba0c48570368f5de2445488c6-998x669.jpg%3Fw%3D628%26h%3D770%26q%3D80%26fit%3Dclip%26auto%3Dformat%26dpr%3D2&w=1920&q=75)
  
  Breakfast
  
  ## Made to Order Breakfast
  
  Indulge in a complimentary, made to order breakfast, crafted to offer a delightful start to your day at the Savannah Sunset Resort & Spa.
  
  ![A fire pit](https://www.sixflags.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fbsnrdz4t%2Fproduction%2F2a20766955cdfa194894f3455d6168eb32909602-3840x2160.jpg%3Fw%3D628%26h%3D770%26q%3D80%26fit%3Dclip%26auto%3Dformat%26dpr%3D2&w=1920&q=75)
  
  Nightly Activities
  
  ## Entertainment
  
  Enjoy outdoor games, a fire pit with marshmallow roasting, and an entertainment space allowing for music, animal encounters, and more.
  
  ![Woman getting a massage](https://www.sixflags.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Fbsnrdz4t%2Fproduction%2Fd577d6a945b0f57984583f4b839e8e284430dbd9-1707x2560.jpg%3Fw%3D628%26h%3D770%26q%3D80%26fit%3Dclip%26auto%3Dformat%26dpr%3D2&w=1920&q=75)
  
  VIP
  
  ## VIP Experience Add-Ons
  
  Various package options exclusive to resort guests including behind-the-scenes encounters and spa treatments may be added to your stay. (only available with two-night stay)
  
