  Great experience all around and we plan to visit in the future. We had good weather as cool at night (didn’t need the AC) and not too hot during the day (we turned on AC). All the service team was friendly and excellent. Special shout-out to our evening server Karl Lloyd who did a great job. We also enjoyed our meals for dinner and breakfast (photos provided). Would highly recommend. We went to the theme park day of (special entrance) and day of checkout as included. Also enjoyed the Giraffe feedings, live band music, Smores/firepit, balcony view of roaming animals that even walked right in front of our tent.
  
  
  
  
  
  
