  [Best trip ever](https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g46528-d28191159-r1061002176-Savannah_Sunset_Resort_Spa-Jackson_New_Jersey.html)
  
  This vacation was the best my Husband and I ever had. From the moment we arrived we were greeted by staff at the front entrance. We felt as if we arrived in Africa. Staff is amazing. Animals are so well cared for. Vip tour was something out of a movie. Tour guides took extra time to explain and answer any questions we had. Glamping tents were luxury all the way. I want to send a special thank you to Liz who made sure we had everything we could possible want or need. Breakfast was very good and dinner was amazing. Entertainment in the evening was wonderful. I would rate this trip a 100. I would also rate Liz a 100. We are in the process of panning a family vacation for next season with my son and his wife.
  
